 2020-00662020-02-06,  GAC,  ,  , 
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of RICHARD BALE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Central African Republic and as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Gabonese Republic, with residence in Yaoundé; SÉBASTIEN BEAULIEU as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guinea, with residence in Dakar; MARK GLAUSER as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Vanuatu, with residence in Canberra; JAMAL KHOKHAR as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to Turkmenistan, with residence in Ankara; PETER MACARTHUR as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of the Philippines; CAMERON MACKAY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste, with residence in Jakarta; and NELL STEWART as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Islamic Republic of Mauritania, with residence in Rabat.
